Link to github repository: 
https://github.com/s3963096/Advanced-Programming-Assignment-2

IDE used: Eclipse
Java Version: used: jdk-20 JavaSE-20
JavaFX Version: JavaFX21
Database used: SQLLITE (DATABASE INCLUDED IN ZIP FOLDER)

To install and run program download the folder from the github repository. Import the entire folder as a project into eclipse and then press run.

For the OOP design of the program I have followed a MVC approach. Models, Views and Controllers are separated. Also I have used a singleton design pattern to
code the JDBCConnection. There will only be one instance of JDBCConnection in the program. I have also used an Abstract class Controller to group all
the attributes that the rest of the controllers share.

Model
	Users
	Posts
	
